1. Ja želim da upoznam novu osobu. (*upoznam*, verb, infinitive) (I want to meet a new person.)
2. On me je upoznao sa svojim prijateljima. (*upoznao*, verb, past tense) (He introduced me to his friends.)
3. Kad sam upoznala svog muža, znala sam da je on prava osoba za mene. (*upoznala*, verb, past tense) (When I met my husband, I knew he was the right person for me.)
4. Da li si ikada upoznao nekoga ko je toliko veseo? (*upoznao*, verb, past tense) (Have you ever met someone who is so cheerful?)
5. Ona je upoznavala nove kulture tokom svog putovanja. (*upoznavala*, verb, past continuous tense) (She was getting to know new cultures during her travels.)
6. Upoznavanje novih ljudi može biti uzbudljivo iskustvo. (*upoznavanje*, noun) (Meeting new people can be an exciting experience.)
7. Želim da se upoznam sa svim članovima tima pre nego što počnemo sa radom. (*upoznam*, verb, present tense) (I want to get to know all the team members before we start working.)